title: Best of CCK: Stripper Stories
description:
Tampa Strip Club manager calls in to let us know the real rules of the club. Dave Portnoy is a HUGE Fat Joe fan, Clinique Happy and Acqua di Gio. The time Stoolies drank everything in the bar except the Hennessy. Edward 40 Hands. Power Hour, Case Race and Century Club.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
